description: Stephanie will not be able to make it to the wedding because of bad weather in Chicago. Phoebe admits to Aly that she lied about Darla’s death and asks for Aly’s forgiveness. Aly forgives Phoebe.  Later, Aly asks Bridget how long she was sad after Nicole died. Ridge and Thorne discuss the unveiling of Forrester Originals. Pam finds the pictures of Thorne and Taylor that Aly colored on. She and Eric decide not to say anything until after the wedding. As Taylor gets ready for the wedding Brooke again questions Taylor’s feelings for Nick. Later, Taylor finds that Aly has cut her wedding dress to shreds. Aly apologizes for ruining the dress but Thorne and Taylor decide they need to postpone the wedding. Donna, Clarke, Storm and Nick discuss the unveiling of the Forrester’s new company. They all decide to stick together to make Forrester Creations a success, no matter what the Forrester’s decide to do. Nick takes a wedding present over to Taylor and is surprised to find her at home. She tells him the wedding is off.  As she cries, he comforts her.
